list.comment: It can take quite some time to guess the right password, so I just added a line to let you know it's working on it.

task.summary: I wanted to make a program that could guess passwords so that a person can try typing in their password and see how safe it is. I have included the 10 000 most common passwords as well from Wikipedia. I am still working on this but since I have a functional program I am saving it now and will make further iterations in the future.

Made some modifications. Now it starts from the lowest number instead of highest (startLength and maxLength) and also tells you how many attempts it took to crack if it didn't find the password in the password.txt file.
It can take quite some time to guess the right password, so I just added a line to let you know it's working on it.
